Why would you think that a lead additive would be benificial?

I use a pint of Marvel Mystery oil in my gas, each fillup---

Great stuff to lubricate, the valves and guide's-----especially durring
the hot summer month's----

Good idea to run it in your oil too---keeps everything, clean and
spinning free inside the engine-----


